typeProperties.script:
source(output(
		PRODUTO_DESC as string,
		MUNICIPIO as string,
		UF as string,
		FANTASIA as string,
		NR_CNPJ as string,
		CNES as integer,
		CID as string,
		QTDE_INICIAL_PACIENTES as integer,
		MS_INICIAL_PACIENTES as decimal(10,0),
		QTDE_PACIENTES_NOVOS as integer,
		QTDE_PACIENTES_RETORNO_MESMA as integer,
		QTDE_PACIENTES_RETORNO_OUTRA as integer,
		QTDE_PACIENTES_VIERAM as integer,
		QTDE_PACIENTES_FORAM as integer,
		QTDE_PACIENTES_DELTA as integer,
		QTDE_PACIENTES_SAIRAM as integer,
		QTDE_MOVIMENTACAO as integer,
		QTDE_FINAL_PACIENTES as integer,
		MS_FINAL_PACIENTES as decimal(10,0),
		PP as string,
		DT_PERIODO_INICIAL as string,
		DT_PERIODO_FINAL as string,
		QTDE_PACIENTES_CONTINUAM as integer,
		MERCADO as string,
		TERRITORIO as string,
		GD as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false,
	inferDriftedColumnTypes: true,
	dateFormats: ['yyyy-MM-dd'],
	timestampFormats: ['yyyy.MM.dd HH:mm:ss'],
	preferredIntegralType: 'integer',
	preferredFractionalType: 'decimal',
	partitionBy('key',
		0,
		PRODUTO_DESC
	)) ~> source1
